# Simple 5K Run Time Calculator

# Ask the user for their pace per kilometer
minutes = int(input("How many minutes per kilometer? "))
seconds = int(input("How many seconds per kilometer? "))

# Calculate total time for 5 km
total_seconds = (minutes * 60 + seconds) * 5
total_minutes = total_seconds // 60
remaining_seconds = total_seconds % 60

# Show the result
print("Your 5K time will be about", int(total_minutes), "minutes and", int(remaining_seconds), "seconds.")
